331
00:21:40,515 --> 00:21:43,309
Whoo-hoo-hoo-hoo!

332
00:21:43,351 --> 00:21:45,978
(West): Antonio!

333
00:21:46,021 --> 00:21:48,897
I have waited to see

334
00:21:48,940 --> 00:21:50,649
